{"tid":1518182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日去基督徒個遊行，但唔好騎劫","createTime":"2019-08-30T07:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T16:31:44.000Z","uid":48039,"like":69,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"64dde48220471c149e9765acc53f8c923b8c06c1","tid":1518182,"uid":48039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:20:30.000Z","msg":"代轉：我們是一群沒有連登account的60後耶撚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1517842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1517842</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我見有唔少巴打絲打都推緊依個Po <br />\n亦知道會有好多人會轉去參加依個遊行<br />\n但我好想千其唔好騎劫個遊行<br />\n同埋希望參加嘅巴絲打會守番人地個規則<br />\n唱下歌點都好<br />\n但唔好令佢地難做<br />\n<br />\n佢地依個時候出個po叫人黎幫手行<br />\n真係已經幫到盡 <br />\n如果我地騎劫左人地個遊行<br />\n啲狗一粒子彈打落去都唔知點算<br />\n雖然話會引起國際關注<br />\n但而家樣樣都引起國際關注架啦<br />\n啲狗有冇理過 政府有冇理過<br />\n<br />\n我唔係唔支持勇武<br />\n但係可以係完左之後先勇武<br />\n遊行期間比番基本嘅尊重人地基督徒<br />\n唔好急於一時 依場係長期戰<br />\n唔洗急於一時同啲狗打對抗<br />\n我地除左要佢地驚<br />\n最主要係唔好再比佢地拉人<br />\n<br />\n希望各位會出席嘅<br />\n和理非又好 勇武又好<br />\n大家合作 <br />\n<br />\n聽日831見 <br />\n<br />\n#weconnect"},{"pid":"94668a21434795d7deb6c1ae86d78ebb90c1b200","tid":1518182,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:20:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k29z7U2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk29z7U2.gif&h=78a316aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=fc0e21f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=950e7459\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=620e999c\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"8747b6100644da302a1d8401b47c0bb058d02761","tid":1518182,"uid":48039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:21:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6059d8fead92909da79d12ff87f5b12eef0b6406","tid":1518182,"uid":37504,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:21:28.000Z","msg":"而家唔勇武都d狗都會射tg 啦"},{"pid":"7e4e7220deee2d83437abe1a191aac39fdb7e0a7","tid":1518182,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:22:50.000Z","msg":"無矛盾 <br />\n行完呢個3點 渣打等<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bdb04cfc35f7475b426ad7cc946db6ad650e2db","tid":1518182,"uid":48039,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"6059d8fead92909da79d12ff87f5b12eef0b6406","tid":1518182,"uid":37504,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:21:28.000Z","msg":"而家唔勇武都d狗都會射tg 啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:23:09.000Z","msg":"我地勇武令基督徒比狗打<br />\n同基督徒和平遊行比狗打<br />\n完全係兩個層面嘅事 <br />\n<br />\n無謂令其他宗教團體覺得係示威者令佢地教從受傷<br />\n咁以後仲邊有人夠膽出黎比個場我地去行"},{"pid":"18011d0fddd8ddf7f8ad02a1851ad0f141963224","tid":1518182,"uid":247699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:23:23.000Z","msg":"體社署外抗議要求支援被捕社工<br />\n2019-08-30 HKT 10:52<br />\n <br />\n反送中社福聯合陣線早上到位於灣仔胡忠大廈的社署總部抗議，要求社署保障被捕社工、支援社工就反修例事件進行的人道救援、以及支援未成年被捕人士等。<br />\n<br />\n有社工說，至今有12名社工在衝突現場進行人道工作時以非法結集罪被捕，他認為警方做法荒謬，應該停止在有社福中心等地方施放催淚煙。<br />\n<br />\n另外，組織表示，早前有年輕示威者在深水埗被捕後，警方拒絕讓社工提供支援及陪同前往警署，他們認為此舉嚴重剝奪對未成年被捕者的支援權利，絕不能夠接受。<br />\n<br />\n現場有數十人參與，又高叫口號，要求社署署長與在場人士公開對話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=1a9ea5fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&h=0c818935\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n由今朝到0830到而家,署長話見又話有誠意。結果餓到我地而家係胡忠8樓,社署點解唔肯見社工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你而家出黎未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5575f2f545738665167769a0ac937026bfd78275","tid":1518182,"uid":270956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:24:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c7f8cde0943a05f4db1dbb9e566e0fdc558d7fe4","tid":1518182,"uid":48039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:24:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b3dcbc382bc80c455665d8a5c28dfa1975cfea","tid":1518182,"uid":48039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:39:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff64041219830a701ff1a10a402aac254b0f05b5","tid":1518182,"uid":83131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:47:33.000Z","msg":"行動Post 推返上頂呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見唔見哩家幾咁黑暗呀!? 黎明就到架喇!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />頂住呀 保持憤怒 never forgive, never forget<img src